According to China Earthquake Networks Center ... Earthquake with magnitude 6 . 6 hits China ; 100 may be dead , injured Times of India - ‎ 12 hours ago ‎ SHANGHAI : About 100 people could have died or been injured in a 6 . 6 magnitude earthquake which struck near Ya ' an city in China ' s southwestern province of Sichuan on Saturday , close to where a massive temblor struck in 2008 , killing almost 70 , 000 .